title: Sibling Watchery - Drag Race UK Season 3 - Episode 7
description:
This week on Watchery, Monét is joined by Lawrence Chaney to discuss Episode 7 of Drag Race UK Season 3 while Bob recovers from surgery. The two dive into what the hell the queens were supposed to do for "Fugly", they break down the worst and best looks of this week and go into who they think the strongest players are, and let's just say things get heated!!

The episode is sponsored by Wondery. Follow “Operator” on Apple Podcasts, Amazon Music, or you can listen early and ad-free by subscribing to Wondery Plus in Apple Podcasts or the Wondery App.
